1074
01:13:54,347 --> 01:13:56,432
I beg you to forgive him.

1075
01:13:56,933 --> 01:13:58,851
Sir, look.

1076
01:13:59,352 --> 01:14:00,519
Look at these.

1077
01:14:02,855 --> 01:14:06,192
Sir, can I ask you to please
forgive him this time?

1078
01:14:06,734 --> 01:14:08,778
