1079
01:14:08,945 --> 01:14:11,030
I swear I'm not lying.

1080
01:14:12,865 --> 01:14:16,577
Sir, since he was fired, he's been depressed.

1081
01:14:16,744 --> 01:14:18,037
He can't help it.

1082
01:14:19,372 --> 01:14:20,706
Sir, you're his elder.

1083
01:14:20,873 --> 01:14:22,124
Please forgive him.

1084
01:14:24,460 --> 01:14:28,422
