1085
01:14:28,714 --> 01:14:30,299
God bless you.

1086
01:14:31,050 --> 01:14:32,385
Don't leave the building.

1087
01:14:32,593 --> 01:14:34,762
No, I'll wait for him to come back.

1088
01:14:38,391 --> 01:14:39,809
Will you ask her?

1089
01:14:41,143 --> 01:14:44,397
