1090
01:14:44,563 --> 01:14:46,232
So let her...

1091
01:14:47,900 --> 01:14:50,236
Dad... Please.

1092
01:14:52,989 --> 01:14:54,031
Okay.

1093
01:14:54,573 --> 01:14:55,825
Promise.

1094
01:14:59,745 --> 01:15:00,913
Why do you promise?

1095
01:15:06,836 --> 01:15:07,920
Dad...

1096
01:15:09,255 --> 01:15:10,256
Yes?

1097
01:15:12,675 --> 01:15:14,468
No, I'll wait for him to come back.

1098
01:15:16,762 --> 01:15:17,805
No.

1099
01:15:20,516 --> 01:15:21,642
Why?

1100
01:15:22,435 --> 01:15:23,477
Nothing.

1101
01:15:24,437 --> 01:15:25,646
So why did you ask?

1102
01:15:27,189 --> 01:15:28,607
Last night, Mom said you knew.

1103
01:15:29,859 --> 01:15:32,361
Where was she to see if I knew?

1104
01:15:33,154 --> 01:15:37,116
She said when you were told that
Razieh's baby had died,

1105
01:15:37,283 --> 01:15:38,868
you didn't say anything.

1106
01:15:39,035 --> 01:15:41,287
You didn't ask if she was pregnant.

1107
01:15:41,662 --> 01:15:43,456
You didn't get surprised.

1108
01:15:44,540 --> 01:15:48,669
At times like this, people usually ask
if she was carrying a child.

1109
01:15:48,836 --> 01:15:50,629
