1110
01:15:54,717 --> 01:15:57,011
Your mom wants to turn you against me.

1111
01:16:13,861 --> 01:16:15,571
Will you ask her?

1112
01:17:14,380 --> 01:17:15,881
I can't.

1113
01:17:17,550 --> 01:17:18,759
Didn't you promise?

1114
01:17:21,595 --> 01:17:22,930
I'm sorry.

1115
01:17:33,315 --> 01:17:35,401
Which step was she on?

1116
01:17:36,277 --> 01:17:37,319
This one.

1117
01:17:37,403 --> 01:17:39,071
- This?
- This one.

1118
01:17:49,957 --> 01:17:52,501
Take Grandpa in. I'll be right back.

1119
01:18:26,911 --> 01:18:28,954
- Are you mad at me?
- No.

1120
01:18:33,500 --> 01:18:35,336
You went upstairs?

1121
01:18:35,878 --> 01:18:38,088
Yes, I went to see Mrs. Kalani.

1122
01:18:39,256 --> 01:18:40,424
What for?

1123
01:18:40,633 --> 01:18:43,886
I told her they are coming to investigate.
To beware.

1124
01:18:44,762 --> 01:18:46,055
Beware of what?

1125
01:18:48,849 --> 01:18:50,434
Beware of...

1126
01:18:51,352 --> 01:18:53,938
That they are coming to investigate.

1127
01:18:54,480 --> 01:18:56,023
Is that not okay?

1128
01:18:56,899 --> 01:19:00,402
If she is to tell the truth,
why should she beware?

1129
01:19:08,369 --> 01:19:10,579
- Termeh. ..
- Yes?

1130
01:19:10,663 --> 01:19:11,830
Come with me.

1131
01:19:11,997 --> 01:19:14,833
- I have homework.
- Leave it for now.

1132
01:19:16,043 --> 01:19:18,128
