1141
01:19:45,072 --> 01:19:47,199
She wouldn't fall like this.

1142
01:19:47,449 --> 01:19:49,660
Imagine you were thrown.
Follow the direction.

1143
01:19:50,202 --> 01:19:52,955
- Then how had she fallen there?
- I don't know.

1144
01:19:53,163 --> 01:19:55,708
I'm just saying
she wasn't thrown on these steps.

1145
01:19:55,874 --> 01:19:57,376
Come and stand here.

1146
01:19:58,127 --> 01:20:00,921
And hit here and then turn
and hit here and fall here.

1147
01:20:01,588 --> 01:20:03,757
I want you to know. Go on.

1148
01:20:18,689 --> 01:20:20,357
Did he throw you in this direction?

1149
01:20:20,524 --> 01:20:22,568
No, towards the lower level.

1150
01:20:22,735 --> 01:20:23,944
You look.

1151
01:20:24,111 --> 01:20:27,364
This door doesn't allow me to
even if I want to. It's not possible.

1152
01:20:27,531 --> 01:20:28,866
Where did you fall down?

1153
01:20:29,033 --> 01:20:31,327
- On these stairs.
- Which step?

1154
01:20:32,119 --> 01:20:33,662
I think it was this one.

1155
01:20:33,871 --> 01:20:35,080
You think or you're sure?

1156
01:20:36,123 --> 01:20:37,541
I'm not sure.

1157
01:20:37,708 --> 01:20:39,543
Ma'am, this is where you found her?

1158
01:20:40,002 --> 01:20:41,837
I didn't see her fall.

1159
01:20:42,004 --> 01:20:44,465
When I got here, she was on that lower step.

1160
01:20:44,631 --> 01:20:46,383
Why don't you say anything?

1161
01:20:46,592 --> 01:20:48,135
Go show them how he threw you.

1162
01:20:48,302 --> 01:20:50,596
I was so sick
I didn't know what happened to me.

1163
01:20:50,804 --> 01:20:53,557
Look, I'll stand in her place.

1164
01:20:53,724 --> 01:20:57,978
You in the doorway
and push me as hard as you want.

1165
01:20:58,145 --> 01:20:59,897
I'm saying it's not possible to fall there.

1166
01:21:00,064 --> 01:21:01,565
Of course you won't fall.

1167
01:21:02,316 --> 01:21:04,401
A pregnant woman falls easily.

1168
01:21:04,902 --> 01:21:07,529
Then you come here.
You choose who pushes you.

1169
01:21:07,696 --> 01:21:09,448
I'm saying it's not possible.

1170
01:21:09,615 --> 01:21:12,576
I'm saying if you push from here,
she won't fall on the stairs.

1171
01:21:13,035 --> 01:21:15,537
What stairs?
She says she fell on that step up there.

1172
01:21:15,788 --> 01:21:18,749
They all say they saw her on that one.

1173
01:21:18,957 --> 01:21:21,043
Ma'am, did you see her get thrown?

1174
01:21:21,293 --> 01:21:23,796
From up there I couldn't see the door,

1175
01:21:23,962 --> 01:21:25,964
but I saw the stairs when she fell.

1176
01:21:26,256 --> 01:21:28,592
Can you show me where you were?

1177
01:21:28,759 --> 01:21:30,386
Maybe she got dizzy and fell.

1178
01:21:30,552 --> 01:21:32,888
How often did you use these stairs?

1179
01:21:33,055 --> 01:21:34,681
Why hadn't she gotten dizzy?

1180
01:21:35,015 --> 01:21:36,058
Excuse me.

1181
01:21:36,225 --> 01:21:39,561
That morning when I saw her here I asked her

1182
01:21:39,978 --> 01:21:42,147
why there was garbage on the steps.

1183
01:21:42,314 --> 01:21:45,859
She said she had gotten dizzy
and dropped the bag.

1184
01:21:46,026 --> 01:21:47,069
Right?

1185
01:21:47,152 --> 01:21:51,156
- She took the garbage down.
- You told me you got dizzy.

1186
01:21:51,281 --> 01:21:54,618
Mrs. Kalani, hadn't she mopped
the stairs that day?

1187
01:21:54,785 --> 01:21:56,870
The stairs were wet. Maybe she slipped.

1188
01:21:57,287 --> 01:21:58,872
You jerk! You made her slip.

1189
01:21:59,081 --> 01:22:00,290
Be respectful!

1190
01:22:00,541 --> 01:22:02,251
I'm polite in front of your family.

1191
01:22:02,418 --> 01:22:04,461
You'd better be polite, you shit!

1192
01:22:05,254 --> 01:22:06,255
Don't cuss.

1193
01:22:06,338 --> 01:22:07,673
