1197
01:22:16,265 --> 01:22:19,017
To hell with me for wasting my time here.

1198
01:22:21,228 --> 01:22:22,229
Excuse me.

1199
01:22:22,312 --> 01:22:23,856
Give us her backpack.

1200
01:22:35,367 --> 01:22:36,660
Here it is...

1201
01:22:47,504 --> 01:22:49,798
Don't you want your drawing book?

1202
01:22:52,217 --> 01:22:54,261
Sweetie, don't be upset

1203
01:22:54,470 --> 01:22:57,139
that I am fighting with your mom and dad...

1204
01:22:57,347 --> 01:22:59,183
Let me put it in your bag.

1205
01:23:06,565 --> 01:23:09,067
My mommy didn't take your money.

1206
01:23:10,277 --> 01:23:11,528
I know.

1207
01:23:12,529 --> 01:23:15,199
That's not why I was fighting with her.

1208
01:23:17,075 --> 01:23:19,077
Then for what?

1209
01:23:20,037 --> 01:23:23,081
I was upset because she left my dad.

1210
01:23:25,834 --> 01:23:28,295
She went to the doctor's.

1211
01:23:33,550 --> 01:23:34,760
Go on.

1212
01:23:37,095 --> 01:23:38,096
Take care.

1213
01:23:38,430 --> 01:23:42,100
According to the court's request,
I'll examine him and write what I see.

1214
01:23:42,267 --> 01:23:46,021
Well, Doctor, you can see
he doesn't talk anymore.

1215
01:23:46,188 --> 01:23:47,981
Didn't you say he has Alzheimer's?

1216
01:23:48,148 --> 01:23:51,527
Yes, but before this happened,
he would speak a bit.

1217
01:23:51,693 --> 01:23:54,988
This is a doctor's office. Prove that in court.

1218
01:23:55,280 --> 01:23:57,074
Does he have any bruising?

1219
01:23:57,616 --> 01:23:59,660
Yes, some.

1220
01:24:36,154 --> 01:24:37,489
What happened?

1221
01:24:38,532 --> 01:24:42,244
I'm not sure the bruising has to do
with when he fell off the bed.

1222
01:24:58,594 --> 01:25:00,137
Don't run.

1223
01:25:00,596 --> 01:25:03,223
Mom, pull the window down.
They're fighting.

1224
01:25:03,432 --> 01:25:05,684
Don't you see this is a girls' school?

1225
01:25:05,851 --> 01:25:08,061
I just have one question for this lady.

1226
01:25:08,228 --> 01:25:10,230
You're not allowed to stand here.

1227
01:25:14,526 --> 01:25:15,569
Take your fight to the police.

1228
01:25:15,777 --> 01:25:17,821
I don't want to fight.
I just want to speak to her.

1229
01:25:18,071 --> 01:25:21,950
I have nothing to say to you.
I don't know you or her husband.

1230
01:25:22,159 --> 01:25:24,661
- Then why did you lie in court?
- What lie?

1231
01:25:24,870 --> 01:25:25,954
She knows what lie.

1232
01:25:26,038 --> 01:25:27,205
Ms. Safaei, call the police.

1233
01:25:28,248 --> 01:25:30,334
Don't scare me with the police.

1234
01:25:30,417 --> 01:25:32,252
She's not involved.

1235
01:25:32,336 --> 01:25:35,130
Then why does she try to get
my daughter to speak?

1236
01:25:35,213 --> 01:25:36,214
I did no such thing.

1237
01:25:36,798 --> 01:25:39,801
You are a teacher. Aren't you ashamed?

1238
01:25:39,968 --> 01:25:43,472
Why did you ask her if I hit her mom
and she lost the baby?

1239
01:25:43,555 --> 01:25:44,598
I never did.

1240
01:25:44,681 --> 01:25:46,892
You pick on a 4-year-old's drawing

1241
01:25:47,059 --> 01:25:50,187
and tell her her dad hit her mom
and she lost the baby?

1242
01:25:50,354 --> 01:25:51,480
I didn't say that!

1243
01:25:51,563 --> 01:25:55,734
Why do you think we beat our wives
and children like animals?

1244
01:25:55,901 --> 01:25:59,071
I swear on this Quran,
we're humans just like you.

1245
01:26:06,828 --> 01:26:09,164
I have nothing to lose.

1246
01:26:09,373 --> 01:26:13,043
Tell your husband
not to make me do something crazy.

1247
01:26:13,460 --> 01:26:15,420
I'll wait by the door.

1248
01:26:18,548 --> 01:26:19,925
I'm unemployed.

1249
01:26:20,092 --> 01:26:22,636
I'll stand out there all clay.
Eventually you'll come out.

1250
01:26:22,803 --> 01:26:24,346
Come to the court and say you lied

1251
01:26:24,513 --> 01:26:27,557
or I'll get to the bottom of what's between
you and her husband.

1252
01:26:27,724 --> 01:26:30,686
Shame on you. I've been patient so far.

1253
01:26:30,852 --> 01:26:32,938
So why are you defending him?

1254
01:26:33,897 --> 01:26:35,273
I told the truth.

1255
01:26:35,440 --> 01:26:36,525
- The truth?
- Yes!

1256
01:26:36,608 --> 01:26:39,569
Place your hand on this and swear.

1257
01:26:39,778 --> 01:26:41,655
Why swear?
What does this have to do with her?

1258
01:26:41,822 --> 01:26:43,949
I'm not scared. What do I have to say?

1259
01:26:44,116 --> 01:26:47,577
You said her husband didn't know
my wife was pregnant.

1260
01:26:47,744 --> 01:26:48,745
- Yes.
- Swear it.

1261
01:26:49,287 --> 01:26:52,124
I swear on this Quran that day at their house,

1262
01:26:52,332 --> 01:26:56,211
