and didn't hear what your wife and I said.

1263
01:26:57,337 --> 01:27:00,132
Okay? Anything else I should say?

1264
01:27:05,053 --> 01:27:06,304
He's crazy.

1265
01:27:09,558 --> 01:27:11,810
Call your husband. Don't go alone.

1266
01:27:12,102 --> 01:27:14,563
No, I don't want him to know. I'm sorry.

1267
01:27:14,730 --> 01:27:17,065
Why are you all standing here?

1268
01:27:18,608 --> 01:27:19,651
Hello?

1269
01:27:21,778 --> 01:27:23,530
Hello, Ms. Qahraei.

1270
01:27:23,947 --> 01:27:27,492
I had left you a message.

1271
01:27:27,659 --> 01:27:29,745
Can you please pick up?

1272
01:27:34,666 --> 01:27:38,336
The lady that took care of my dad,

1273
01:27:38,503 --> 01:27:42,466
apparently that day you gave her
the number for a gynecologist.

1274
01:27:42,632 --> 01:27:45,886
I wanted to ask you for that number to call

1275
01:27:46,052 --> 01:27:49,514
and see if she went
to see the doctor that week

1276
01:27:49,681 --> 01:27:51,975
and what her problem was.

1277
01:27:52,476 --> 01:27:55,228
I would appreciate you calling me back.
Thank you.

1278
01:28:10,994 --> 01:28:12,913
What do you want to do?

1279
01:28:14,414 --> 01:28:15,707
With what?

1280
01:28:17,000 --> 01:28:19,252
