Every day a new fight?

1281
01:28:19,795 --> 01:28:21,129
Why? What happened?

1282
01:28:21,379 --> 01:28:25,175
He went to her school today
and embarrassed her in front of everyone.

1283
01:28:27,844 --> 01:28:29,346
What did he say?

1284
01:28:29,763 --> 01:28:34,059
He screamed, "Her dad killed my child."

1285
01:28:36,436 --> 01:28:38,647
How can she go back to that school?

1286
01:28:39,564 --> 01:28:41,775
Do you know what you are doing?

1287
01:28:42,400 --> 01:28:43,652
What I am doing?

1288
01:28:47,781 --> 01:28:49,074
He's making threats.

1289
01:28:49,282 --> 01:28:50,617
He wouldn't dare!

1290
01:28:52,619 --> 01:28:54,287
Termeh, go to your room.

1291
01:29:00,710 --> 01:29:03,171
