on her way to school?

1292
01:29:04,589 --> 01:29:06,091
What do you want me to do?

1293
01:29:06,299 --> 01:29:07,759
Run off abroad with you?

1294
01:29:07,968 --> 01:29:11,263
To hell with abroad.
Why can't you talk normally?

1295
01:29:11,429 --> 01:29:15,392
This is about Termeh
and the situation you've put her in.

1296
01:29:15,559 --> 01:29:17,185
I've put her in?

1297
01:29:17,769 --> 01:29:20,188
You have some nerve accusing me!

1298
01:29:20,355 --> 01:29:21,857
Who left home?

1299
01:29:22,274 --> 01:29:23,650
Who filed for a divorce?

1300
01:29:23,859 --> 01:29:25,151
You said leave whenever you want.

1301
01:29:25,235 --> 01:29:26,987
Why did you come back?

1302
01:29:27,195 --> 01:29:29,281
I didn't. I'm here because of her situation.

1303
01:29:29,489 --> 01:29:30,532
Her situation's fine.

1304
01:29:30,615 --> 01:29:33,702
- You have two choices...
- Don't try to intimidate me.

1305
01:29:33,869 --> 01:29:35,120
What intimidation?

1306
01:29:36,121 --> 01:29:38,248
