He doesn't even speak anymore.

1315
01:30:00,812 --> 01:30:02,731
He didn't speak much before.

1316
01:30:02,898 --> 01:30:05,609
I was happy with the few words he spoke.

1317
01:30:05,901 --> 01:30:07,527
Is it as bad as losing a baby?

1318
01:30:07,611 --> 01:30:10,113
