There might be a chance that
her husband did something

1321
01:30:18,413 --> 01:30:21,166
and now she wants to blame me.

1322
01:30:21,333 --> 01:30:24,002
Her child said that day
she had gone to the doctor.

1323
01:30:24,169 --> 01:30:27,839
Why couldn't she wait two hours
to go to the doctor?

1324
01:30:28,006 --> 01:30:30,508
Why did she tie the old man
to his bed and leave?

1325
01:30:30,675 --> 01:30:32,844
The examiner said
her child died due to a blow.

1326
01:30:33,011 --> 01:30:36,056
How do we know it was a blow from me?

1327
01:30:36,598 --> 01:30:39,684
I won't accept it till it's been proven to me.

1328
01:30:42,270 --> 01:30:44,564
Fine, let me take Termeh.

1329
01:30:44,731 --> 01:30:48,193
Shame on you
for putting pressure on me now.

1330
01:30:48,360 --> 01:30:49,486
I am worried about her.

1331
01:30:49,569 --> 01:30:52,614
Your child wants to live here.
She has to stay here and learn.

1332
01:30:52,822 --> 01:30:55,116
Learn what? Fighting and obstinacy?

1333
01:30:55,283 --> 01:30:57,661
To learn not to be a coward like you

1334
01:30:57,827 --> 01:31:00,372
who gives in so easily.

1335
01:31:00,664 --> 01:31:03,833
He knows who to frighten.
Why doesn't he threaten me?

1336
01:31:04,042 --> 01:31:05,043
Yes, I'm a coward.

1337
01:31:05,710 --> 01:31:09,089
Your whole life,

1338
01:31:09,255 --> 01:31:11,633
instead of solving problems,

1339
01:31:11,841 --> 01:31:16,554
you've either run away or
raised your hands and given in.

1340
01:31:16,805 --> 01:31:20,350
Just say why you want to leave this country.

1341
01:31:20,517 --> 01:31:21,810
You're afraid to stay.

1342
01:31:22,394 --> 01:31:25,313
I was gone one week
and you couldn't manage.

1343
01:31:25,397 --> 01:31:27,399
I couldn't manage and I'm responsible.

1344
01:31:28,441 --> 01:31:31,945
Give me Termeh and you do what you want.

1345
01:31:34,823 --> 01:31:37,242
Termeh, sweetie, you don't have to stay.

1346
01:31:37,325 --> 01:31:39,035
Go wherever you like.

1347
01:31:44,541 --> 01:31:46,501
You still don't want to come?

1348
01:31:57,721 --> 01:31:59,431
"He sells it for 20 a kilo.

1349
01:31:59,597 --> 01:32:03,601
"If every day he sells 270 kilos..." Write 270.

1350
01:32:05,979 --> 01:32:10,025
Then, how much profit
does he make in one day?

1351
01:32:11,026 --> 01:32:12,736
How do you solve this?

1352
01:32:13,236 --> 01:32:14,946
Did you lie?

1353
01:32:16,698 --> 01:32:17,866
What?

1354
01:32:19,367 --> 01:32:20,493
Did you lie?

1355
01:32:22,120 --> 01:32:23,329
About what?

1356
01:32:25,165 --> 01:32:28,668
When you said
you didn't know she was pregnant.

1357
01:32:29,919 --> 01:32:31,129
Why?

1358
01:32:32,881 --> 01:32:37,802
You said that you didn't hear Ms. Qahraei
and Razieh speaking.

1359
01:32:37,886 --> 01:32:38,887
Yes.

1360
01:32:39,554 --> 01:32:44,267
Then how did you know that
Ms. Qahraei gave her the number?

1361
01:32:45,310 --> 01:32:47,771
Didn't she say it at the same time?

1362
01:32:56,112 --> 01:32:57,822
Okay.

1363
01:32:59,032 --> 01:33:01,993
If we want to calculate the profit...

1364
01:33:07,957 --> 01:33:09,042
Yes, I knew.

1365
01:33:11,586 --> 01:33:13,630
Your mom was telling the truth.

1366
01:33:15,965 --> 01:33:21,054
When they were talking in the hall,
I heard everything from the kitchen.

1367
01:33:22,388 --> 01:33:24,390
Then why did you say you didn't?

1368
01:33:27,936 --> 01:33:30,939
Do you know what would happen
if I said I knew?

1369
01:33:34,192 --> 01:33:36,861
One and a half to three years in prison.

1370
01:33:38,154 --> 01:33:41,825
I only thought of what would happen to you,

1371
01:33:42,325 --> 01:33:44,119
who you'd stay with.

1372
01:33:45,078 --> 01:33:46,913
I said I didn't know.

1373
01:33:49,749 --> 01:33:51,751
If you knew, why did you hit her?

1374
01:33:51,918 --> 01:33:55,672
I knew she was pregnant
but at that moment I didn't.

1375
01:33:55,839 --> 01:33:58,716
I had forgotten it- I wasn't paying attention-.

1376
01:34:04,973 --> 01:34:06,933
So tell them this.

1377
01:34:10,770 --> 01:34:13,148
The law doesn't care about this.

1378
01:34:13,773 --> 01:34:16,234
Either I knew or I didn't...

1379
01:34:23,366 --> 01:34:24,659
Look at me.

1380
01:34:25,785 --> 01:34:28,413
If you want me to I'll tell them.

1381
01:35:21,925 --> 01:35:22,967
Hi.

1382
01:35:28,473 --> 01:35:31,017
Didn't I say not to come to the front?

1383
01:35:51,955 --> 01:35:53,206
Ms. Qahraei!

1384
01:36:04,926 --> 01:36:06,094
What are you doing?

1385
01:36:06,552 --> 01:36:09,013
Ms. Qahraei, wait...

1386
01:36:10,056 --> 01:36:13,851
if you pull over
I'll just explain something to you.

1387
01:36:14,310 --> 01:36:15,561
Please let me...

1388
01:36:17,021 --> 01:36:18,189
Dad!

1389
01:36:21,776 --> 01:36:23,486
Who's responsible for my child's safety now?

1390
01:36:23,653 --> 01:36:25,321
Without a witness there's no case.

1391
01:36:25,488 --> 01:36:28,741
Hi.

1392
01:36:28,825 --> 01:36:30,285
And then come to you?

1393
01:36:30,493 --> 01:36:32,912
How should I know you are telling the truth?

1394
01:36:33,079 --> 01:36:34,789
Why should I lie?

1395
01:36:34,998 --> 01:36:38,084
Bring my daughter and father here
just to lie?

1396
01:36:38,501 --> 01:36:40,545
- Is she here now?
- Yes, outside.

1397
01:36:40,628 --> 01:36:42,672
Ask her yourself.

1398
01:36:42,839 --> 01:36:47,260
I'm afraid to leave her at school.
I'm afraid to leave my dad at home.

1399
01:36:47,802 --> 01:36:49,387
Is the plaintiff here?

1400
01:36:50,722 --> 01:36:52,056
Did you finish writing?

1401
01:36:52,223 --> 01:36:53,308
Almost.

1402
01:36:54,267 --> 01:36:56,185
You didn't know his wife was pregnant?

1403
01:36:56,352 --> 01:36:57,603
No, I didn't.

1404
01:36:57,770 --> 01:37:01,274
When she was speaking to the tutor,
you didn't hear them?

1405
01:37:01,441 --> 01:37:02,525
No, I didn't.

1406
01:37:03,693 --> 01:37:05,069
You didn't, huh?

1407
01:37:05,778 --> 01:37:07,780
What I'm saying is...

1408
01:37:08,031 --> 01:37:10,450
The tutor came and revoked her testimony.

1409
01:37:11,075 --> 01:37:12,785
She says you knew.

1410
01:37:13,202 --> 01:37:15,663
- She said I knew?
- Yes, she came yesterday.

1411
01:37:15,830 --> 01:37:17,415
He threatened her...

1412
01:37:17,623 --> 01:37:19,751
Answer me. Did you hear her or not?

1413
01:37:19,917 --> 01:37:21,419
I said no.

1414
01:37:21,586 --> 01:37:23,629
How did you know
about the doctor's number?

1415
01:37:23,838 --> 01:37:25,048
My daughter told me.

1416
01:37:25,214 --> 01:37:26,466
What did she tell you?

1417
01:37:26,674 --> 01:37:28,843
That she got the number from her teacher.

1418
01:37:30,011 --> 01:37:31,888
Go tell her to come in.

1419
01:37:33,181 --> 01:37:34,515
Now?

1420
01:37:35,391 --> 01:37:36,851
And wait outside.

1421
01:37:37,852 --> 01:37:39,228
What question?

1422
01:37:43,941 --> 01:37:45,735
What does he want to ask?

1423
01:37:48,488 --> 01:37:50,615
I don't know. Give me that.

1424
01:37:58,331 --> 01:38:00,124
So what do you have to say?

1425
01:38:00,291 --> 01:38:02,001
You haven't asked me anything.

1426
01:38:02,794 --> 01:38:05,338
Didn't your dad tell you
what I want to ask you?

1427
01:38:05,630 --> 01:38:06,631
No.

1428
01:38:06,839 --> 01:38:08,132
What grade are you in school?

1429
01:38:08,633 --> 01:38:09,884
Sixth.

1430
01:38:10,051 --> 01:38:13,471
The day your tutor came to your house

1431
01:38:13,638 --> 01:38:16,474
and asked the lady about her pregnancy,

1432
01:38:17,058 --> 01:38:18,726
were you there?

1433
01:38:18,976 --> 01:38:22,688
Not then, I had gone to get my books.

1434
01:38:23,189 --> 01:38:27,652
Then how did you know
she got the doctor's number from your tutor?

1435
01:38:28,736 --> 01:38:32,407
She gave her the number later,
when she was leaving.

1436
01:38:32,573 --> 01:38:33,866
In front of you?

1437
01:38:34,367 --> 01:38:35,410
Yes.

1438
01:38:35,493 --> 01:38:36,994
Why didn't you tell your dad sooner?

1439
01:38:37,370 --> 01:38:38,371
What?

1440
01:38:38,663 --> 01:38:42,166
That she got the doctor's number
from your tutor.

1441
01:38:42,333 --> 01:38:45,336
I didn't think it was important
for my dad to know.

1442
01:38:47,839 --> 01:38:50,341
And did you tell your dad or did he hear it?

1443
01:38:51,092 --> 01:38:54,887
That she gave the number? I told him.

1444
01:38:55,513 --> 01:38:57,515
- You told him?
- Yes.

1445
01:38:59,350 --> 01:39:00,518
Okay.

1446
01:39:51,736 --> 01:39:53,488
What crime did I commit?

1447
01:39:53,654 --> 01:39:54,739
Nothing. You're right.

1448
01:39:55,740 --> 01:39:57,658
He's not accepting his responsibility.

1449
01:39:57,825 --> 01:40:00,912
I admit that he's to blame,
but in the end what will happen?

1450
01:40:01,078 --> 01:40:05,625
One or two years in court
for a payment plan of the blood money.

1451
01:40:05,791 --> 01:40:08,085
But why? That's what upsets me.

1452
01:40:08,252 --> 01:40:10,171
Why do you think it's for the money?

1453
01:40:10,421 --> 01:40:11,672
When did I say such a thing?

1454
01:40:11,756 --> 01:40:16,344
You think I am a bum and my kid died
and I don't understand anything.

1455
01:40:16,511 --> 01:40:18,179
I never said anything like that.

1456
01:40:18,262 --> 01:40:19,931
Let's see what she's saying.

1457
01:40:20,473 --> 01:40:21,474
There's no other way.

1458
01:40:22,308 --> 01:40:24,435
Your child won't come back.

1459
01:40:24,602 --> 01:40:26,604
I admit that he's to blame,
but in the end what will happen?

1460
01:40:26,771 --> 01:40:29,148
Her husband didn't do it on purpose.

1461
01:40:29,774 --> 01:40:32,985
They're good people
for giving you a solution.

1462
01:40:33,152 --> 01:40:36,656
Take the money and settle it.
You can use it in your situation.

1463
01:40:36,948 --> 01:40:40,993
Right now we'll decide on an amount
and I'll get my husband's approval.

1464
01:40:42,787 --> 01:40:46,165
Now we have to get his approval?
For God's sake leave us alone.

1465
01:40:49,293 --> 01:40:51,462
You act like you don't need the money.

1466
01:40:51,629 --> 01:40:52,838
Take a look at yourself.

1467
01:40:53,005 --> 01:40:54,632
Don't let him go.

1468
01:40:58,803 --> 01:41:00,972
Wait a second. I want to talk to you.

1469
01:41:51,606 --> 01:41:52,940
Will you stay?

1470
01:41:55,693 --> 01:41:56,694
Mom...

1471
01:41:59,363 --> 01:42:01,365
Let me speak to him.

1472
01:42:11,042 --> 01:42:13,044
Come sit. I want to talk to you.

1473
01:42:15,588 --> 01:42:16,589
I can hear you.

1474
01:42:19,216 --> 01:42:22,470
I went and spoke to her husband today.

1475
01:42:23,220 --> 01:42:24,555
Sit down.

1476
01:42:35,399 --> 01:42:36,776
I managed

1477
01:42:36,984 --> 01:42:38,778
to get him to agree

1478
01:42:39,737 --> 01:42:42,239
to take 15 million instead of 40 million.

1479
01:42:42,406 --> 01:42:45,493
Three five-million checks
in exchange for his consent.

1480
01:42:45,910 --> 01:42:47,578
How dare you speak to him about money?

1481
01:42:48,496 --> 01:42:50,247
I can't handle the stress of my child's safety.

1482
01:42:50,414 --> 01:42:51,957
You don't get it.

1483
01:42:52,124 --> 01:42:54,960
Just now when you were late,
I was worried sick.

1484
01:42:55,169 --> 01:42:57,755
Why are you interfering?

1485
01:42:58,756 --> 01:43:00,424
I didn't come here to fight.

1486
01:43:00,758 --> 01:43:02,760
Oh, God, why can't I make her understand?

1487
01:43:02,927 --> 01:43:06,514
Didn't you say it was my fault,
that I introduced her,

1488
01:43:06,764 --> 01:43:09,767
that if I hadn't left,
none of this would've happened?

1489
01:43:09,934 --> 01:43:11,435
So let me fix it, then.

1490
01:43:11,936 --> 01:43:15,106
If I pay, it means
I have accepted it was my fault.

1491
01:43:15,314 --> 01:43:16,357
But he has consented.

1492
01:43:16,440 --> 01:43:17,858
He won't let us be.

1493
01:43:18,109 --> 01:43:20,695
- He won't, anyway.
- Why should I bribe him?

1494
01:43:20,861 --> 01:43:22,446
Think of it as my dower money.

1495
01:43:23,114 --> 01:43:26,492
If I had to I would beg and borrow

1496
01:43:26,867 --> 01:43:28,661
to get your dower money.

1497
01:43:28,869 --> 01:43:31,622
But I don't have the money
to pay for extortion.

1498
01:43:31,831 --> 01:43:35,459
Our child is going through adolescence.
She is suffering.

1499
01:43:37,128 --> 01:43:41,882
So you understand
the sensitivity of her adolescence.

1500
01:43:42,216 --> 01:43:43,968
If she was suffering
she wouldn't have stayed.

1501
01:43:44,552 --> 01:43:46,470
Why do you think she stayed?

1502
01:43:47,221 --> 01:43:48,806
Did she choose you?

1503
01:43:50,641 --> 01:43:52,560
To keep us from separating.

1504
01:43:54,812 --> 01:43:56,564
She knows I won't go anywhere without her.

1505
01:43:59,191 --> 01:44:01,986
She is suffering but she doesn't show it.

1506
01:44:06,407 --> 01:44:08,993
Call them now and say I won't pay

1507
01:44:09,160 --> 01:44:11,996
until it's been proved to me
that I am responsible.

1508
01:44:12,163 --> 01:44:13,748
I'll sell my car.

1509
01:44:14,874 --> 01:44:16,500
Don't sell it for my sake.

1510
01:44:16,667 --> 01:44:18,085
It's not for you.

1511
01:44:18,252 --> 01:44:20,504
If your child is not worth...

1512
01:44:20,671 --> 01:44:23,674
Why are you talking nonsense?
Money's not the issue.

1513
01:44:23,883 --> 01:44:27,094
I won't rest till my child's safety
is guaranteed.

1514
01:44:27,511 --> 01:44:29,930
You don't have the right to do anything.

1515
01:44:30,097 --> 01:44:31,348
Understand?

1516
01:44:32,016 --> 01:44:34,769
If I had done nothing you would be in prison.

1517
01:44:38,898 --> 01:44:41,442
Come to court and get back the bail.

1518
01:44:42,026 --> 01:44:44,278
I don't want to be out because of it.

1519
01:45:03,088 --> 01:45:04,256
Get up, Termeh.

1520
01:45:05,382 --> 01:45:06,550
Get up, let's go.

1521
01:45:06,717 --> 01:45:08,052
Get up, I tell you.

1522
01:45:08,219 --> 01:45:09,386
Mom, please.

1523
01:45:11,972 --> 01:45:13,599
I don't want you to stay here.

1524
01:45:13,974 --> 01:45:15,142
No, Mom, I won't let you.

1525
01:45:15,309 --> 01:45:19,146
Is 15 million more important
than your child's life?

1526
01:45:19,313 --> 01:45:20,731
I won't let you do this.

1527
01:45:20,898 --> 01:45:22,733
If your child is not important...

1528
01:45:22,900 --> 01:45:25,611
Mom, please listen, why are you doing this?

1529
01:45:25,778 --> 01:45:27,112
You said you would stay.

1530
01:45:27,279 --> 01:45:28,405
I was stupid!

1531
01:45:30,407 --> 01:45:32,034
Mom, please...

1532
01:45:32,117 --> 01:45:33,452
I'll wait in the car.

1533
01:45:44,630 --> 01:45:48,592
Go there for a few days
till your exams are finished.

1534
01:45:49,301 --> 01:45:50,970
Your grandparents are there.

1535
01:45:51,846 --> 01:45:53,472
You'll have more fun.

1536
01:45:53,764 --> 01:45:55,516
Didn't you say it's not serious?

1537
01:45:56,642 --> 01:45:58,143
It got serious.

1538
01:45:59,770 --> 01:46:00,938
Termeh...

1539
01:46:01,856 --> 01:46:02,940
Honey...

1540
01:46:05,025 --> 01:46:06,861
If you cry I'll cry, too.

1541
01:46:07,027 --> 01:46:09,446
Why won't you pay them
so she'll come back?

1542
01:46:10,030 --> 01:46:12,449
This has nothing to do with her coming back.

1543
01:46:12,616 --> 01:46:14,994
It does. She had come to stay.

1544
01:46:15,202 --> 01:46:17,621
Her stuff was in the car, I saw it.

1545
01:46:58,078 --> 01:47:01,332
If you think I am guilty, go get your mom.

1546
01:47:01,498 --> 01:47:04,001
We'll call them and go pay them.

1547
01:48:20,911 --> 01:48:22,287
I have doubts.

1548
01:48:22,454 --> 01:48:24,039
Didn't he throw you?

1549
01:48:24,790 --> 01:48:25,791
Yes.

1550
01:48:26,917 --> 01:48:28,919
Did something happen at home?

1551
01:48:30,421 --> 01:48:32,423
No. Even before, my child wasn't moving.

1552
01:48:34,091 --> 01:48:35,634
Before he threw you?

1553
01:48:41,765 --> 01:48:43,976
You mean your child had already died?

1554
01:48:44,810 --> 01:48:47,146
I don't know. Maybe.

1555
01:48:47,312 --> 01:48:48,939
Had something happened?

1556
01:48:51,275 --> 01:48:54,945
I'm not sure, but the night before, I had pain.

1557
01:48:56,488 --> 01:48:58,949
- Have you ever lost a baby before?
- No.

1558
01:49:02,286 --> 01:49:03,662
I was hit by a car.

1559
01:49:10,961 --> 01:49:14,465
Your father-in-law had gone into the street.

1560
01:49:14,631 --> 01:49:16,008
I went after him.

1561
01:49:17,301 --> 01:49:19,762
He was crossing the street to come back.

1562
01:49:19,928 --> 01:49:23,974
I ran to stop him but I got hit instead.

1563
01:49:24,683 --> 01:49:26,643
The pain started that night.

1564
01:49:29,855 --> 01:49:31,190
Does your husband know this?

1565
01:49:33,650 --> 01:49:35,611
Why don't you come say this in court?

1566
01:49:38,280 --> 01:49:42,117
My husband will kill me
if he finds out I told you this.

1567
01:49:43,660 --> 01:49:46,830
Since yesterday
when he promised his creditors,

1568
01:49:46,997 --> 01:49:48,165
he's been waiting.

1569
01:49:49,500 --> 01:49:53,045
What do we have to do with all this?

1570
01:49:56,298 --> 01:49:57,883
It's my fault.

1571
01:50:01,970 --> 01:50:05,849
Yesterday when he said
you'd promised him this money,

1572
01:50:06,016 --> 01:50:08,519
I got really scared. I called a few people.

1573
01:50:09,144 --> 01:50:11,855
They say if I have doubts
then it's a sin to take it.

1574
01:50:13,357 --> 01:50:16,193
If we don't pay
my husband's innocence must be proved.

1575
01:50:16,693 --> 01:50:20,197
Why don't you come say this in court?

1576
01:50:20,364 --> 01:50:22,491
But your husband won't leave us alone.

1577
01:50:23,033 --> 01:50:24,409
I fear for my child.

1578
01:50:24,576 --> 01:50:29,164
I'm afraid that if I take this money,
something will happen to my child.

1579
01:50:29,331 --> 01:50:31,041
What do you want me to do?

1580
01:50:32,543 --> 01:50:34,169
Don't pay this money.

1581
01:50:35,587 --> 01:50:36,588
Don't.

1582
01:50:44,388 --> 01:50:46,557
Will your husband leave us alone?

1583
01:51:19,798 --> 01:51:22,551
Give me that. Bring some plates.

1584
01:51:23,594 --> 01:51:25,929
Don't worry. Nothing will happen.

1585
01:51:47,075 --> 01:51:50,078
When you revoke your complaint,

1586
01:51:50,287 --> 01:51:53,415
we'll give you these three checks.

1587
01:51:53,582 --> 01:51:54,917
God bless you.

1588
01:51:55,000 --> 01:51:59,922
Hojjat, get a pen and paper
so we can write everything down and sign it.

1589
01:52:01,131 --> 01:52:02,466
I want to say something first...

1590
01:52:02,633 --> 01:52:04,468
Say a prayer and finish it.

1591
01:52:04,635 --> 01:52:07,804
I have already agreed
and will honor my word.

1592
01:52:07,971 --> 01:52:13,268
I just want his wife
and my daughter to be here when I speak.

1593
01:52:15,812 --> 01:52:17,105
Where is she?

1594
01:52:19,524 --> 01:52:20,859
Thank you.

1595
01:52:21,777 --> 01:52:23,320
Please, also call my daughter.

1596
01:52:27,658 --> 01:52:29,785
Come in. Your father wants you.

1597
01:52:39,836 --> 01:52:41,672
Termeh, come and sit here.

1598
01:52:42,005 --> 01:52:43,674
Excuse me, sir.

1599
01:52:54,685 --> 01:52:56,186
Look...

1600
01:52:56,353 --> 01:52:59,564
I wrote the checks and I'll give them to you.

1601
01:53:00,148 --> 01:53:01,483
There's no problem.

1602
01:53:01,900 --> 01:53:03,193
I need to ask a favor.

1603
01:53:04,569 --> 01:53:07,030
Ma'am, you are a devout person.

1604
01:53:08,198 --> 01:53:11,702
Swear on the Quran
that I caused your miscarriage.

1605
01:53:20,836 --> 01:53:21,837
Bring a Quran.

1606
01:53:22,879 --> 01:53:24,339
Go get it.

1607
01:53:41,606 --> 01:53:44,359
Come quickly or they'll suspect something.

1608
01:53:45,777 --> 01:53:48,113
His creditors are here for the money.

1609
01:53:48,280 --> 01:53:50,282
You'll ruin our reputation.

1610
01:53:52,409 --> 01:53:54,286
I won't swear.

1611
01:53:55,787 --> 01:53:59,750
Didn't you say you went to get his father
and a car hit you?

1612
01:54:01,418 --> 01:54:03,086
Why aren't you coming?

1613
01:54:04,212 --> 01:54:05,922
She's afraid to swear.

1614
01:54:07,132 --> 01:54:08,258
Why?

1615
01:54:08,425 --> 01:54:12,054
I... I have doubts.

1616
01:54:18,060 --> 01:54:19,269
Oh, God...

1617
01:54:20,937 --> 01:54:22,731
Azam, go sit with them.

1618
01:54:26,443 --> 01:54:30,322
Why are you saying this now?

1619
01:54:30,947 --> 01:54:33,283
I swear I told Azam.

1620
01:54:34,618 --> 01:54:37,162
Tell me exactly what happened.

1621
01:54:40,290 --> 01:54:43,126
The day before, a car hit me.

1622
01:54:43,752 --> 01:54:46,421
And that night I had a lot of pain.

1623
01:54:56,306 --> 01:54:58,809
- Let's go, it'll be my sin.
- No.

1624
01:54:59,434 --> 01:55:00,852
It's a sin. I asked.

1625
01:55:01,019 --> 01:55:03,980
What sin? He's consented. Let's go.

1626
01:55:04,147 --> 01:55:07,109
I am scared we'll be punished.

1627
01:55:07,275 --> 01:55:10,487
More punished than this?
Look at my situation.

1628
01:55:10,654 --> 01:55:14,199
Have mercy on me. On our child.

1629
01:55:14,366 --> 01:55:17,953
I'm afraid of something happening
to our child.

1630
01:55:18,370 --> 01:55:19,621
Let's go.

1631
01:55:19,788 --> 01:55:20,872
I can't.

1632
01:55:21,039 --> 01:55:22,332
Let's go.

1633
01:55:25,168 --> 01:55:26,795
I can't.

1634
01:55:31,174 --> 01:55:33,343
Don't hit yourself!

1635
01:55:52,821 --> 01:55:56,700
Why did you come here tonight?
Didn't I tell you not to come?

1636
01:55:57,492 --> 01:55:59,703
Didn't I say we don't want your money?

1637
01:56:00,162 --> 01:56:02,539
How will I live in this house?

1638
01:56:03,707 --> 01:56:06,209
Why did you do this to me?

1639
01:57:33,630 --> 01:57:34,673
Come on.

1640
01:57:39,970 --> 01:57:41,471
Let's go.

1641
01:57:57,529 --> 01:57:58,989
Hello. Come in.

1642
01:58:09,040 --> 01:58:10,834
So what's your decision?

1643
01:58:11,501 --> 01:58:16,798
Your parents have left it up to you to decide
who you want to live with.

1644
01:58:16,965 --> 01:58:19,509
With your father or your mother?

1645
01:58:21,011 --> 01:58:22,387
Have you decided?

1646
01:58:22,512 --> 01:58:23,555
Yes.

1647
01:58:24,139 --> 01:58:25,849
- Have you?
- Yes.

1648
01:58:36,693 --> 01:58:38,361
Have you decided or not?

1649
01:58:38,528 --> 01:58:39,529
Yes.

1650
01:58:42,032 --> 01:58:43,658
And what is it?

1651
01:58:45,493 --> 01:58:47,329
Do I have to say it now?

1652
01:58:48,538 --> 01:58:51,374
- If you haven't decided...
- Yes, I have.

1653
01:58:55,920 --> 01:58:58,465
- If you haven't decided yet...
-l have.

1654
01:58:58,548 --> 01:58:59,549
And?

1655
01:59:00,884 --> 01:59:03,720
Would you prefer them to wait outside?

1656
01:59:05,055 --> 01:59:06,514
Can they?

1657
01:59:07,557 --> 01:59:09,684
Sir, wait outside for a minute.

1658
01:59:11,853 --> 01:59:12,854
You, too, ma'am.

